37079>>>>>    Function IsLoggedIn Returns Boolean
37081>>>>>        String sLoginName
37081>>>>>        Boolean bLogWebSession bLoggedIn
37081>>>>>        
37081>>>>>        Get pbLogWebSession to bLogWebSession
37082>>>>>        If not bLogWebSession Begin
37084>>>>>            Forward Get IsLoggedIn to bLoggedIn
37086>>>>>            Function_Return bLoggedIn
37087>>>>>        End
