37549>>>    Procedure OnNavigateForward tWebNavigateData NavigateData Integer hoInvokingView Integer hoInvokingObject
37552>>>        WebSet pbRender of oNewButton to True
37553>>>        WebSet pbRender of oDetailButton to True
37554>>>
37554>>>        Case Begin
37554>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromParent)
37556>>>                // If from parent, this is a constrained drill down
37556>>>                Case Break
37557>>>
37557>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromChild)
37560>>>                // If from child, this is a probably a parent lookup from a Zoom
37560>>>                Case Break
37561>>>
37561>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromMain)
37564>>>                // If from main, this is a probably a main-file lookup from a Zoom
37564>>>                WebSet pbRender of oDetailButton to False
